Comment_contributor: lit. one finger remaining; i.e., one finger of the hand is not used when counting
lit. one hand whole, thus five fingers
lit. the other hand one, thus five plus one
lit. the other hand two, thus five plus two
of the other hand one finger left
lit. two hands all the way, all fingers
from the feet one big toe
from the foot one toe left
from the other foot one toe left

Value: mban amnuk am, mbeị amnuk am takas
Comment_contributor: both hands and both feet completely
Comment_glosser: ‘hand two both foot two both all’
